      <title>交易员权衡日美辩论 日元兑美元领涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/yen-gains-to-strongest-since-jan-2-after-boj-official-speaks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者对日本央行董事会成员的言论和美国总统辩论做出反应，日元领涨其他货币兑美元，抹去了今年的损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/yen-gains-to-strongest-since-jan-2-after-boj-official-speaks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 01:56:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行委员暗示仍有可能加息，日元上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/boj-board-member-signals-rate-hike-is-on-table-if-outlook-met</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行委员中川顺子发表评论称，只要经济表现符合预期，日本央行将继续调整政策，这一言论推动日元升至今年最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/boj-board-member-signals-rate-hike-is-on-table-if-outlook-met</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 01:56:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>需求担忧加剧油价跌势，油价稳定在 70 美元以下</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/oil-stages-rebound-after-global-demand-concerns-trigger-rout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对全球需求的担忧迅速升级，引发了油价迅速而强劲的抛售，导致布伦特原油价格两年多来首次跌破每桶 70 美元，随后油价趋于稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/oil-stages-rebound-after-global-demand-concerns-trigger-rout</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 23:27:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>焦点转向美国 CPI，股市下跌，日元飙升：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，美国和欧洲股票期货下跌，债券期货上涨，原因是美国通胀报告出炉前人们对经济增长的担忧加剧。日本央行官员暗示将进一步加息，日元上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 22:53:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>宝马召回和大众裁员威胁加剧德国工业危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/bmw-cuts-guidance-after-faulty-components-prompt-recall</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国汽车制造商正陷入更深的危机，损害该国最重要行业的未来，宝马汽车公司警告称，利润将受到代价高昂的刹车问题的冲击，大众汽车公司则取消了员工三十年来享受的就业保障。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/bmw-cuts-guidance-after-faulty-components-prompt-recall</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 10:56:45 GMT</pubDate>
